<p>
	This lovely deck of tarot cards was created by the artist Antonio Lupatelli who illustrates that although barely riding up above the ground, the gnomes possess profound wisdom. The cards of the little people are the most sought-after cards by children and adults alike because they open the doors to the magical and wonderful world of the gnomes, our funny friends who are low in stature but high in wisdom. The seventy-eight Arcana are cheerful and enchanting cards, capable of telling beautiful stories while entertaining and teaching. This fantastic deck of tarot cards features 78 divining tarot cards&nbsp;in the size of 44mm x 80mm making it the perfect tool to carry in your pocket and use whenever, wherever.</p>
